{"tid":1945677,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"居港台妹表示：武漢肺炎就是武漢肺炎啦！","createTime":"2020-03-27T08:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:14:46.000Z","uid":309875,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2cd2d2dca09e82dce56fe453ec4e7a7559f5da","tid":1945677,"uid":309875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AtxmJijuzTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAtxmJijuzTg&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=5fcb2a3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AtxmJijuzTg</a><br />\n這個大陸妹是在哈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗆台灣網友斷網？被斷網的應該是你們吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG、推特、Facebook、Youtube、Google、還有一堆不能搜索的字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次在各種大陸被禁的社交網站看到小粉紅翻牆出來的留言反擊<br />\n我就覺得真是辛苦你們了<br />\n如果你們沒有被禁被斷網，你們哪裡需要翻牆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n翻牆去看鍾明軒、波特王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (啊忘了波特王在大陸網站也被禁了那你們是&hellip;&hellip;？)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎就是武漢肺炎</span></span></strong><br />\n是哪裡有問題？歧視武漢？<br />\n那非洲豬瘟德國麻疹日本腦炎中東呼吸綜合症是？？？<br />\n就你大陸人問題最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個名稱是不是歧視，除了文字(text)本身，更多是語境(context) 的問題，<br />\n舉個例子，智障的文字本身就不是一個歧視的名稱，<br />\n但用來罵人(語境)就是暗示對智障人士的輕蔑態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">從武漢爆發出來的不叫武漢肺炎是要叫甚麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n還有中國的新增病例並沒有包括台灣的<br />\n所以意思就是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">台灣不是中國的一個省份</span></strong></span><br />\n從來不存在甚麼台獨<br />\n因為台灣從來不屬於中國<br />\n如果疫病是從台灣傳出來而用台灣(病名)來稱呼<br />\n才不會有那麼多台灣人出來靠杯唉唉叫<br />\n就中國大陸問題最多<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連說習大大跟維尼熊的樣子一樣很可愛喔都不行</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不要來台灣自由行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我很高興的好ㄇ"},{"pid":"5e60260d0caa0d88b37b65847f905d83497f688c","tid":1945677,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"好想去台灣"},{"pid":"72ec589f04305f175b1af822458cc3a681056578","tid":1945677,"uid":309875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e60260d0caa0d88b37b65847f905d83497f688c","tid":1945677,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"好想去台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"之前有去過嗎？<br />\n香港也有些台式餐廳不過味道還是不是那個味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b473e17731783ea50af9d7d868b6905fa2700eee","tid":1945677,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎 <br />\n中國肺炎<br />\n中共肺炎<br />\nChinese virus<br />\nChina virus<br />\nWuhan virus<br />\nCcp virus<br />\n隨便啦<br />\n新冠肺炎不了 日本新冠町表示不滿"}]}